data.description: Spacious 3 bedroom/2 bath well kept double wide Manufactured home located in the charming area of Bayside, TX.  There are wonderful water views right off of the front porch!  As you enter, you will immediately feel right at home with the wood burning fireplace in the spacious open living area.  You will have plenty of room to spread out, as this is a 1680 square foot home!  The owner's suite has it's own bathroom with a separate tub & shower.  This home is located on 3 lots, and comes with 2 storage sheds and a detached garage with an air conditioned workshop/office.  You will be within walking distance to the bay, with a community pier and park at your fingertips.  This would make a fabulous getaway or permanent home.  Offered partially furnished and includes a large Cannon safe as well as all appliances including washer, dryer, refrigerator, stove &  freezer.  The home even has a fresh coat of paint!  Schedule an appointment with your favorite Realtor today!  $5000 flooring allowance
